explanation: [0-0] The video starts in a living room where three young people are standing in a row. The girl in the middle is wearing a pink dress and high heels, while the boys on both sides are dressed in casual light shirts and jeans. There is a white sofa behind them.

[0-9] The girl stands confidently in the middle with her arms crossed and a smile on her face. The two boys on both sides sway their bodies to the music and point at the girl, seemingly interacting with her. Immediately afterwards, the girl starts dancing to the rhythm of the music, crossing her hands at her waist and swaying from side to side. Her movements are full of energy, and her face is filled with a happy smile. The two boys on both sides cooperate with her movements and continue to sway their bodies. Then they turn their backs at the same time, pat their hips with their hands, and continue to wriggle to the music. The two boys danced even more excitedly, with larger movements. At this time, only the girl turned back and started to squat down. She put her index finger on her lips and made a "hush" gesture. The two boys turned their backs to the camera and continued to dance excitedly.
